data.description: Private serene Country Living located 5 minutes from Historic Warwick Village, where you'll find artisanal food and wine with quaint shopping. Approximately an hour away from NYC, your stress will melt away as you drive past your own personal apple trees and onto your 4+ opulent acres. Nestled in the woods, your new 4,700+ sq ft home features an oversized kitchen with center island, large family room with fireplace and wet bar, spacious dining room, 1/2 bathroom, mudroom/laundry room, bonus room, office space, and a tranquil two-sectioned sun room.  On the second floor you'll find a primary bedroom with walk-in closet and full bathroom, 3 additional bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, and an entertainment style family room with full bar and separate entrance from the 3 car garage. Plenty of storage in the full basement with access from the foyer or outside Bilco doors with an additional shed. The backyard and rear patio are ideal for entertaining small or large gatherings.
